cz.ive.template
Class TemplateMap

java.lang.Object
  cz.ive.template.TemplateMap
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class TemplateMap
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

TemplateMap is a serializable singleton used for storing and mapping various templates by their string names. Reason for just another singleton map is in the option to exclude it from saving and loading process since its contents are only loaded during BigLoad and then remains the same. But This is now only an option, TemplateMap is implemented to undergo normal serialization process now.

Author:
ondra
